                        <interp inst="t18360229-name-912" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE FOSTER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. On Thursday morning the 1st of March, I was sent for by Mr. Clark, of South-Street, Chelsea—I took this waistcoat and the prisoner—he said he said he had taken the shoes and lent them to a young man—he afterwards said he sold them for 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. to a young man, but he did not know his name.</p>
